cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.CC, cs.CR

The paper deals with the formalism of abductive reasoning, which is a fundamental concept in artificial intelligence (AI). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI. The paper also involves a thorough analysis of the complexity of the problem, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Additionally, the paper deals with constraint satisfaction problems, which could place it in cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
